Localization.Name: Taftan Boots Shale
Localization.Description: Strong, practical, and stylish, these high-cut boots with reinforced straps will be just the thing you need for those long outdoor treks. The slip- and abrasion-resistant soles were constructed from a proprietary composite of recycled plastic and rubber to improve traction without sacrificing flexibility.
